{"type": "article", "id": 21295, "title": "触摸感应式台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-26T08:23:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702112941myCLIjcbezXQTqSU.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是意大利设计师 odo fioravanti 最新推出的 LED 台灯，可以通过灯前的触摸感应器开关灯并调节灯光强弱。台灯的两个手臂都非常纤细，是用压铸铝材制成，能够灵活调整方向，适应工作和研究的环境，简单而优雅。它另有一款是钉在墙上的，目前还没有出售，<a href=\"http://www.fioravanti.eu/project/Volee\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150857LTyFREtmDs6ZhXwo.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"504\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150857hmkRAvULw68nxSBc.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"484\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59168704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150858sC4TRgYxtZc7d8GX.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"580\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150858oDEwSAyIn27tcaUu.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"511\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}